{"tid":777982,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] 想玩Game識朋友? BOWHK等緊你","createTime":"2018-08-13T10:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T04:49:05.000Z","uid":164307,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0614205fe24cd813d52965e8f78a2bdf87694c","tid":777982,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"Brotherhood of Wolf [BOWHK]，又名狼群，於2018年正式創立既遊戲團隊，致力為香港同澳門等廣東話玩家提供多元化遊戲平台。終極目標係聚集一班志同道合既兄弟，一齊奮鬥，一齊娛樂，為打機而打機。雖然聽落有少少中二病，但我哋就係咁既存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/184205_0e737feeb84edbc4689c51e206221f7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F184205_0e737feeb84edbc4689c51e206221f7f.jpg&h=d562cfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟們既遊戲種類非常繁多，生存射擊模擬策略樣樣齊。<br />\nArma3<br />\nRainbowSix<br />\nPUBG<br />\nWarThunder<br />\nWarframe<br />\nCOH2<br />\nWargame: Red Dragon<br />\nHeroes &amp; Generals<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n所以你一定能夠揾到臭味相投既兄弟們。我哋擁有屬於自己既server，可以提供不同遊戲使用，但暫時仍然進行不定時測試。我哋主要既交流平台响Discord和Teamspeak，所以請玩家先自行安裝呢兩個軟件方便聯絡。兄弟會鼓勵玩家不論平日或假日都上線吹下水打下機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;&lsquo;Wer nicht vorw&auml;rts geht, der kommt zur&uuml;cke&rsquo;&rsquo;係我哋團隊宗旨，呢句話出自德國文學家歌德，中文解釋為「假如你不在前進，你正在倒退中」，我哋亦希望玩家能夠同兄弟會邁步向前。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友仔可以响我哋Facebook page直接pm。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BOWGAMINGHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBOWGAMINGHK&d=YrxRAFvHh%2BjiZ2DXrFK85k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b2a9dfa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BOWGAMINGHK</a>"},{"pid":"0d7a1daf396a2df6c0efeaee8ee832b5ffd30e6c","tid":777982,"uid":164307,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">---下面係團友既藝術創作---</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/185948_e49d9373f2a59baba2c37724805f5cc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F185948_e49d9373f2a59baba2c37724805f5cc0.jpg&h=3a7d5033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/185948_0b7902dec779fe83ac5a62b4784c76a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F185948_0b7902dec779fe83ac5a62b4784c76a5.jpg&h=c5e8b139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/185948_ddc22d7ecce666d1ba93f49878e94fed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F185948_ddc22d7ecce666d1ba93f49878e94fed.jpg&h=c352d456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">---Youtube channel---</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W3GHr4C01_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW3GHr4C01_Q&d=YrxRAFvHh%2BjiZ2DXrFK85k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5ccfc31c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W3GHr4C01_Q</a>"},{"pid":"c9b5209f24bde099295697f418372cffaf1c10c5","tid":777982,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b722b954d2ab7845275d3cf1828d717d7d5f1418","tid":777982,"uid":201946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class